For 'All Labels' widget, show also 'Other Apps' icon, so all apps are accessible.
Allow to star app in its label edit dialog.

AppCacheDao.createObject(): Fix column no mismatch.

They said many times - don't use magic numbers...
Add ability to star/unstar app directly from widget context menu.

Close widget window only if user clearly taps outside of it.

Don't close it of user taps on the header, or if user misses slightly
when tapping on star icon, etc.
Set default export file name as 'backup.txt'.

Use base cursor class for operations.

Otherwise we get cast exception with new MergeCursor usage, etc.
Rename app package away from upstream.

Disable integration with proprietary tool - doesn't play well with pkg rename.

And so useful to maintain it.
